{"tid":1838380,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"中銀，我屌你老母呀！","createTime":"2020-01-24T04:02:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T13:25:43.000Z","uid":323832,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6967f7694cdbfedbebc385f92a9efbb8b50e8da6","tid":1838380,"uid":323832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T04:02:23.000Z","msg":"其實早係12月尾見到中銀俾人裝修，已經同中銀講轉倉，做曬手續<br />\n今朝check番渣打個投資戶口，發現中銀無我Ｄ貨俾渣打。<br />\n於是去番中銀問，再做多次，再交表俾渣打。<br />\n渣打果邊話俾我聽，中銀漏寫聯絡人資料＋電話。<br />\n好！當我唔小心無睇到～<br />\n再去多次，填曬Ｄ聯絡人資料＋電話。<br />\n再番去渣打，點知新北江果間中銀無寫中央結算編號俾我！<br />\n仆佢個臭街！<br />\n我Ｅ家熨到火屎甘，又要我去多次！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！"},{"pid":"9f215120be388f2b0d979bf6b5e8ba1fc4a3e31b","tid":1838380,"uid":239842,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T04:03:57.000Z","msg":"得啦得啦係人都知你住天水圍啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd825af0acd6a48aadb42abde179d66c8ea97dbb","tid":1838380,"uid":78304,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:15:53.000Z","msg":"早係12月尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n7月我已經轉走晒所有錢<br />\n你自己本身都戇鳩<br />\n12月1月一堆公眾假期你都唔識提早做<br />\n又唔識跟緊D<br />\n<br />\n抵你用支銀"},{"pid":"1c12767666ebd490b1e43358f1afcac2d1e04e17","tid":1838380,"uid":59608,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:48:24.000Z","msg":"12月尾?<br />\n<br />\n坐左幾多年"},{"pid":"21b521219e21c12d64cddae99aba31ad21178a7a","tid":1838380,"uid":76591,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:49:30.000Z","msg":"得啦得啦，知你住天水圍啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fc11a6b2ddb2b1e5a907ab31d5